snippet.title: GOLDEN – K-Pop Demon Hunters | Emotional Cover by Emma Heesters (Huntr/X, Ejae, Audrey Nuna)
snippet.description:
I had so much fun pouring my heart into this cover of “GOLDEN” – the powerful anthem from KPop Demon Hunters, originally performed by Huntr/X and voiced by the incredible Ejae, Audrey Nuna, and Rei Ami. It’s one of those rare songs that builds with emotion and energy in such a cinematic way – I just had to make it my own 🥺✨

🎧 Stream GOLDEN and explore more from me: https://link.tristarrecords.uk/emmaheesters/listen
🔥 Watch more genre-bending collabs & covers: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLMDOg4hOhCgp3wXCx87f5K03zqFT6jO6r
💥 Subscribe and support my channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/emmaheesters?sub_confirmation=1

Huge thanks to the original writers for creating such a beautiful song – I hope I did it justice 💛

If this cover moved you, drop me a comment – I read them all and love hearing what parts connected with you 💬

🎥 Video filmed by Mike Attinger

Lyrics to the song:

I was a ghost, I was alone, hah
Eoduwojin apgilsoge (Ah)
Given the throne, I didn't know how to believe
I was the queen that I'm meant to be
I lived two lives, tried to play both sides
But I couldn't find my own place
Called a problem child 'cause I got too wild
But now that's how I'm getting paid, kkeuteopsi on stage

I'm done hiding, now I'm shining like I'm born to be
We're dreaming hard, we came so far, now I believe

We're goin' up, up, up, it's our moment
You know together we're glowin'
Gonna be, gonna be golden
Oh, up, up, up with our voices
Yeongwonhi kkaejil su eomneun
Gonna be, gonna be golden

Oh, I'm done hidin' now I'm shinin' like I'm born to be
Oh, our time, no fears, no lies
That's who we're born to be

Waited so long to break these walls down
To wake up and feel like me
Put these patterns all in the past now
And finally live like the girl they all see

No more hiding, I'll be shining like I'm born to be
'Cause we are hunters, voices strong, and I know I believe

We're goin' up, up, up, it's our moment
You know together we're glowing
Gonna be, gonna be golden
Oh, up, up, up, with our voices
Yeongwonhi kkaejil su eomneun
Gonna be, gonna be golden

Oh, I'm done hidin', now I'm shining like I'm born to be
Oh, our time, no fears, no lies
That's who we're born to be

You know we're gonna be, gonna be golden
We're gonna be, gonna be
Born to be, born to be glowin'
Balge binnaneun uri
You know that it's our time, no fears, no lies
That's who we're born to be

 ♡ DONATE TO CHARITY BELOW ♡

Cancer Research Institute: https://www.cancerresearch.org
